DarkenedRoom darkened_weave
 with	description
	[;
	    if (ContainsLight(player))
		"The passage undulates as it moves west to east, 
		curving back and forth with a kind of reassuring 
		regularity. The walls are rough here, as if the 
		passage had just been carved hours ago.";
	    else
		"The passage runs at odd angles -- you keep one hand 
