		"For a second, you really consider doing it. But you
		stop yourself -- this is insanity...";
	    }
	    else
	    {
		deadflag = DEAD_CUBICLE;
		"The feeling of nothingness is... comfortable? It
		doesn't feel like falling, doesn't feel like you may
		die at any moment --";
	    };

	 Search:
	    <<Examine self>>;
	],
	after
